        {
            "title": "東京通脹降溫幅度超預期 料無阻日本央行進一步加息",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 東京通脹降溫幅度超出預期，食品和能源價格壓力緩解，但這不太可能阻止<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:日本央行;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/日本央行\">日本央行</a>進一步加息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本總務省周五公佈的數據顯示，12月東京不含生鮮食品的消費者價格指數同比上漲2.3%，漲幅較上月的2.8%大幅回落。這也是8月以來增速首次放緩，主要反映食品價格漲幅收窄及能源成本下降。經濟學家此前預計該數據將放緩至2.5%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">整體通脹指標從前月的2.7%放緩至2%，而剔除能源價格的指標放緩至2.6%。東京通膨數據是衡量日本全國物價趨勢的領先指標。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2c1cfa1e-42dc-30ae-8d11-699bc39dc761-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/uIsiEDsKZ5Fy7ZNgL4p8Ow--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/191d80e6947a6844d33aba8149c456b0\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周五數據發布之際，市場正密切關注日本物價走勢，以判斷下次政策調整的時機。上周，日本央行政策委員會一致投票決定加息至1995年以來的最高水平0.75%。行長植田和男在決策後的新聞發布會上稱，如果價格展望實現，將進一步收緊貨幣政策，但未具體說明收緊的速度或終端利率水平。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">接受彭博調查的經濟學家預計，日本央行的加息頻率大概在每六個月一次，終端利率料達到1.25%左右。這意味著分析人士預計在本輪緊縮周期中，還將再加息兩次左右。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Tokyo Inflation Cools More Than Expected as BOJ Watches (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E9%99%8D%E6%BA%AB%E5%B9%85%E5%BA%A6%E8%B6%85%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F-%E6%96%99%E7%84%A1%E9%98%BB%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E9%80%B2-%E6%AD%A5%E5%8A%A0%E6%81%AF-001812594.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-26 10:41:03",
