        {
            "title": "美國要求阿富汗移民在聖誕節和元旦報到",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 作為川普政府整頓<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:阿富汗;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/阿富汗\">阿富汗</a>移民的最新舉措，美國移民和海關執法局(<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:ICE;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/ICE\">ICE</a>)在假日季傳喚了居住在美國的阿富汗人、要求他們出示證件。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據彭博新聞社看到的、許多人收到的信件的副本，ICE正在安排「按計畫報到」預約，其中一封信要求在聖誕節當天會面，另一封則要求在元旦當天。其他通知則要求在12月27日和30日報到。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">ICE已經逮捕過應這種正式要求前往其辦公室的移民，其中包括前去參加綠卡面談的人。這些信件的收件人此前已獲得法律保護，被視為「阿富汗友人」 —— 因為前總統喬·拜登2021年8月發起一個項目，以保護那些在美軍撤出阿富汗、塔利班隨後接管這個飽受戰爭蹂躪的國家後逃往美國的人。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2bc59599-5186-325f-9fe5-a909bb0b2e7d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「ICE乘聯邦和宗教節日拘留阿富汗人，這種時候他們獲得法律諮詢、法院和人權倡議人士幫助的機會最為匱乏，」非營利組織AfghanEvac的創始人Shawn VanDiver在批評這些傳喚行動及其時機的聲明中表示。「這並非例行的行政日程。」AfghanEvac為曾協助美國武裝行動的阿富汗人提供支持。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而，一位國土安全部發言人稱，這些報到是「例行」且「一直都有」的，但並未詳細說明發出了多少封信件。該發言人還補充說，ICE在假期期間會繼續執行常規工作。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聖誕節和元旦是聯邦假日，大多數政府機關都關閉。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Tells Afghan Migrants to Report on Christmas, New Year’s Day</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Alicia A. Caldwell.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E9%98%BF%E5%AF%8C%E6%B1%97%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%A8%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95%E7%AF%80%E5%92%8C%E5%85%83%E6%97%A6%E5%A0%B1%E5%88%B0-012629577.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-26 10:01:02",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "植田和男對實現價格目標更有信心 暗示明年有望進一步加息",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 日本央行行長植田和男對該行更接近實現其可持續通膨目標的信心增強，暗示明年可能進一步加息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「伴隨工資成長，2%的價格穩定目標正穩步接近實現，」植田和男周四在商業游說團體經團聯主辦的會議上發表講話時稱。「近年來，在勞動力市場趨緊的背景下，企業在設定工資和價格方面的行為發生了顯著變化。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這可能是植田和男今年的最後一次公開講話，強化了投資者對儘管上周五日本央行已將借貸成本上調至1995年以來最高水平，但加息周期尚未結束的預期。交易員們正在尋找有關下次加息時點的線索，而植田和男的語氣比上周政策決定後的新聞發布會略顯鷹派。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-030ce307-3977-3fee-8d9c-eab964eeb9f4-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他重申經濟展望若實現，央行將提高利率，並指出實際利率仍處於非常低的水平。根據彭博最近的調查，大多數日本央行觀察人士預計未來的加息頻率為每六個月一次。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「工資和物價溫和上漲的機制很可能在明年及以後得到保持，」植田和男稱。「因此，央行基線預測實現的可能性似乎正在上升。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他表示，商業行為的變化表明經濟日益強勁。他指出，隨著通膨持續走高，家庭和企業的價格預期不斷上升，企業將成本轉嫁給消費者的現象已變得越來越普遍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「日本經濟回歸所謂零常態狀態（即工資和物價幾乎不變的狀態）的可能性似乎已經大大降低，」他說。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Ueda Signals Further Hikes With More Confidence Over Price Goal</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%A4%8D%E7%94%B0%E5%92%8C%E7%94%B7%E5%B0%8D%E5%AF%A6%E7%8F%BE%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99%E6%9B%B4%E6%9C%89%E4%BF%A1%E5%BF%83-%E6%9A%97%E7%A4%BA%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E9%80%B2-%E6%AD%A5%E5%8A%A0%E6%81%AF-070233326.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-25 16:15:45",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國呼籲柬埔寨和泰國結束持續數周的致命暴力衝突",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國國務卿馬爾科·盧比奧呼籲<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:柬埔寨;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/柬埔寨\">柬埔寨</a>和泰國停止暴力衝突。當前兩國正繼續進行談判，以結束持續數周的致命衝突。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據美國周四的聲明，盧比奧在與柬埔寨首相洪瑪奈的通話中，重申美國總統唐納德·川普希望雙方實現和平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國國務院發言人Tommy Pigott在聲明中表示：「盧比奧國務卿進一步重申，美國準備為柬埔寨和泰國之間的對話提供便利，以確保兩國之間的和平與穩定。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自12月7日衝突再次爆發以來，泰國和柬埔寨正首次展開對話。衝突已造成至少44人死亡，超過50萬平民流離失所。之前在7月份持續五天的衝突最終在馬來西亞和美國的斡旋下達成初步停火協議。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0a119938-7806-31f6-8dc0-8225b806d72b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：泰國和柬埔寨即將進行和平談判 泰方提出幾項要求</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Urges Cambodia and Thailand to End Weeks of Deadly Violence</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E6%9F%AC%E5%9F%94%E5%AF%A8%E5%92%8C%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%B5%90%E6%9D%9F%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E6%95%B8%E5%91%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%87%B4%E5%91%BD%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-231035050.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-26 08:10:42",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "特朗普支持的候選人贏得宏都拉斯總統大選",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 經過漫長而混亂的計票過程之後，宏都拉斯總統大選終於宣布一位保守派候選人獲勝，這位候選人得到美國總統特朗普的支持。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">選舉當局周三宣布，納斯裡·「蒂托」·阿斯富拉贏得了11月30日的選舉，他以微弱優勢擊敗了電視名人薩爾瓦多·納斯魯拉。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據選舉機構網站公佈的最新計票結果，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:阿斯富拉;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/阿斯富拉\">阿斯富拉</a>獲得40.3%的選票，納斯魯拉獲得39.5%的選票。執政黨候選人裡克西·蒙卡達位列第三，得票19.2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">選舉機構花了三周多的時間才宣布結果，在此期間，納斯魯拉和蒙卡達都指控選舉存在舞弊行為。結果公佈之後，納斯魯拉已表示不會承認敗選，將通過合法、和平方式「捍衛」選舉。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5b543dc9-1c98-3e09-b569-aa2330837652-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">結果在聖誕前日下午公佈，許多宏都拉斯人正在與家人團聚，因此短期內發生動亂的可能性不大。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">67歲的阿斯富拉曾承諾切斷與北京和委內瑞拉的關係，並與「友邦三角」——美國、台灣和以色列——建立密切關係。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國國務卿馬爾科·盧比奧迅速向阿斯富拉表示祝賀，他在X上發帖稱，美國「期待與他的政府合作，促進我們半球的繁榮與安全」。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"納斯裡·阿斯富拉攝影：Tomas Ayuso/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CICum5I1Qprsg6GpfhWIag--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/e8a25ea423d13be193d2f6636602c44a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">納斯裡·阿斯富拉攝影：Tomas Ayuso/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump-Backed Construction Magnate Wins Honduras Election (2)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Jose Orozco、Maya Averbuch.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%9A%84%E5%80%99%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%BA%E8%B4%8F%E5%BE%97%E5%AE%8F%E9%83%BD%E6%8B%89%E6%96%AF%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8-233829671.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-25 12:46:04",
